@taos・79 ☯️ **Weekly update will be pushed to tomorrow** to allow some extra time for finalizing testing on the simulator and validator optimizations; we are also still investigating further refinements to speed up query times as this currently presents somewhat of a bottleneck in enabling to dramatically increase the rate of simulation progression and start to scale up the book count.

This update will not contain any major changes at the level of the incentive mechanism, and only some minor tweaks to the parameters of the background model in the simulation, so should not expect any substantial action to be required in terms of strategy development.  **The update does however modify the synapse structure and miners should be aware that they will need to upgrade to the latest version when released**.  This does not affect the usage of the synapse data in agent logic, so no other changes are expected to be required.

We will announce more details of the changes during the day tomorrow, and will notify when pushed and deployed (tomorrow ~17:00 UTC).

